question: Who has been recently crowned Miss World Asia 2019?
explanation:
Jamaica\'s Toni-Ann Singh was crowned Miss World at an annual beauty pageant held at the 69th annual beauty pageant held in ExceL London, UK on 14 December. She was crowned by the 2018 winner Vanessa Ponce de Leon of Mexico. She became the fourth Jamaican woman to win Miss World. 
India\'s Suman Rao became the second runners-up. She was crowned as Miss World Asia.
